These template tags are always available to you in smarty

{$http_link} - Link to your document root. Useful for creating links and finding css files
{$http_images} - Link to the main images folder


The following tags need to be implemented in your template somewhere to work. There is functionality in the Template class to use them right now

{$tplHead} - Add additional content between the <head> tags. Template->AddHead($string)
